{
  "texts": [
    "The tracker outputs the confidence score of sampled candidates and chooses the best matching patch as the target.",
    "Various patch sampling methods are exploited, e.g., sliding window [53], particle filter [41,48], and Gaussian sampling [11].",
    "A crucial task is to utilize powerful features to represent the target.",
    "Emerging convolution networks have enabled more trackers to be built via efficient CNNs.",
    "The various frameworks are introduced in the following paragraphs."
  ]
}